name: Cake Covering/Decorating Class - 11th Dec 'Little Garden' Cake
description: ONE SPOT LEFT DATE: Wednesday Dec 11th 2013 - SOLD OUT TOPIC: ‘Little Garden’ cake – fondant cake covering and decorating class. Max class size 5 pax. LOCATION: East Coast Singapore, exact location to be advised once booked TIME: 10.30 am DURATION: Approx 5 hours LEARN: Cover a cake smoothly with fondant. Then decorate the cake in the ‘Little Garden’ design (pictured). You will make the following: Rolled ruffled flowers, leaves, mushrooms, picket fence, ladybug, bee, dragonfly, caterpillar, small blossom flowers, butterfly. This is a very hands on, intensive class. In this class you will also learn how to: Cover a cake board with fondant Use cutters to create shapes Use edible ink pens Use an imprint mat to create wood effect Properly store your cake Provided: 6" Cake or dummy cake supplied or you may bring in your own small cake (6-8") All materials including fondant, gum paste, cake board, food colouring and cake box. Tools to share. Notes to take home. Bring: Packed lunch (coffee/tea/water provided). Take home: A ‘Little Garden’ design cake and a certificate. As an added bonus, you will receive recipes that I use to make butter cake, chocolate cake, buttercream and ganache. Trainer: Wynona Leach Founder of Red Carousel I specialize in novelty cakes for birthdays, which can be viewed here I write tutorials for Cakejournal and recently had recipes included in Young Parents Magazine (Singapore). In the past I have taught sewing to adults for Notebook magazine and have had craft projects published in books and magazines. I have completed PME and Wilton Cake decorating courses.

name: Cake Decorating Class: Figurine Modelling Topper

The Lunch Punch® is intended for use by adults but can be used by children over 3 with adult supervision.

Assorted shapes to suit different party themes.

Imported from Australia, this vibrant collection is brought to you by designer partyware brand, Paper Eskimo.  The entire range is perfectly coordinated and will add that special touch to your table. Choose your selection from the drop down menu.

Plates: Pack includes 12 paper plates. Size 9" (23cm)

Cups: Pack includes 12 paper cups. Size 9oz (250ml)

Napkins: Premium 3ply napkins designed with coordinating patterns on both sides. Pack includes 20 napkins. Napkin folded size: 4.7" x 4.7" (12cm x 12cm).

Check out other matching items in the Paper Eskimo range. Lovely to mix and match colours.
